Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,780)\fad(1321,1000)\3a&00&\3c&0000A0&}调停者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:13.00,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:16.23,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:20.05,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思うまま書き滑らせて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:25.02,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}描く未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:33.59,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}澄み渡る空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:37.10,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}果てしないほど青く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:41.12,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無邪気な心に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.34,0:01:44.72,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充たされ魅かれてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:48.68,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やがて自由に飛びまわれる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:51.72,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}翼を手に入れて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:56.22,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無垢な瞳は求めてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:02:00.02,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}空の向こうへ　行きたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:03.12,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}止め処ない願いから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:06.47,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一つだけ叶うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.57,0:02:10.21,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰にも譲りたくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.28,0:02:14.21,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夢を掴みたいと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:17.42,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.66,0:02:20.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.92,0:02:24.62,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつまでも描き続けられた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:29.72,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}願う未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:13.00,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童时的那个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:16.23,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:20.05,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}随心所欲地去描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:25.02,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己描绘的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:33.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}万里无云的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:37.10,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无边无际的蔚蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:41.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}纯洁无瑕的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.34,0:01:44.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充盈着无限魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:48.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}终于能自由翱翔于天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:51.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}长出了美丽的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:56.22,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无瑕的瞳孔在寻求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:02:00.02,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想去那天空的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:03.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在那无数的愿望中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:06.47,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}若是只有一个能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.57,0:02:10.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我不愿让给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.28,0:02:14.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要紧紧抓住那梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:17.42,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童时的那个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.66,0:02:20.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.92,0:02:24.62,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}永不停息地去描写
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:29.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己祈愿的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.60,0:23:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,780)\fad(1000,8)\3a&00&\3c&0000A0&}禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:43.53,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}炎さえも凍てついた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:50.19,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孤独の中求む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:58.85,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}魂から結びつき
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:06.88,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私を恋い暖めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:15.70,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　祈りの言葉がふるえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.04,0:22:23.41,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　弱きいのちが消えても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.12,0:22:31.28,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえす　輪廻の流れ辿り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:39.90,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終わらない世界の宿命を見つめてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:47.40,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえし　詠われる者達よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.41,0:22:55.54,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}守られてまどろむ宵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:43.53,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就算火焰都冻结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:50.19,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}也在孤独中寻求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:58.85,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}请用灵魂连结我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:06.88,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}请用爱恋温暖我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:15.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}呜呼 那颤抖的祈愿之声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.04,0:22:23.41,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}呜呼 那脆弱的生命消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.12,0:22:31.28,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}追溯那不断交替的轮回之流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:39.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}凝望那永不终结的世界的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:47.40,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不断轮回的 那些传颂之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.41,0:22:55.54,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}被守护着安眠的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可以的话 还是希望能够在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们本来就是在雅玛优拉土生土长的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 死的时候也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露 别吃些奇怪的东西 把肚子吃坏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露 别太勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦的时候 就坦白发泄出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.82,0:01:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs48}注：白皇，哈克奥罗建国后正式的封号，在日文中与“哈克奥罗”读音相同。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白皇 出廷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向您报告
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌帕克河堤修复工程已大致完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿图城塞提出申请 希望增派人手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 您真的不去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢那种氛围
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 我来宣读最后一个报告
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐在睡梦中笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.39,0:03:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那所谓的大神教会是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:04:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身居我们的大神 「解放者」的总寺院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时又自称是调停者的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调停者？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神教会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将调停国家或部族间纷争及防止灾难发生视为己任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此他们巡视各地 如果必要 会对某事加以干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是所谓的调停者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 白皇大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次我们奉大神教会之命出任使节
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫乌露特莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫蒙特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦各位远道而来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常欢迎乌露特莉王女的光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知王女前来我国有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友好？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里还有如此可爱的女官呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌露特莉阁下 艾露露是我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是皇后大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.23,0:05:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我还是独身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子就如同我妹妹一般
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粗茶一杯 不成敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人 很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们并不受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这茶的冲泡手法真高明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这种茶称为粗茶真是太谦虚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白皇大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您同意 我希望能够参观一下城里居民的生活情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就由我来为您领路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣上还有许多政务要忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么让艾露露代替我为您领路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是繁荣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有着其它地方所没有的活力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从压迫中解脱出来 能够安心经商了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 顽皮小鬼 你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 只是蒙特的一两根羽毛而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是艾露露小姐的房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.84,0:07:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露小姐是药师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾想成为药师 为此去学习医术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌露特莉大人您？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我还不清楚自己的立场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您为什么想成为药师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想救助受了伤的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的祖母 曾经是药师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分受到大家的爱戴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也想成为像祖母那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 看得到神结我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.81,0:10:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（咒文）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子应该成功隐身了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆库鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆库鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露 为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和爸爸睡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奥罗大人 抱歉这么晚还来打扰您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有没有来过一位银发的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛觉得有一股很熟悉的波动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神结 快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神结 为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为因为 总是姐姐你 太不公平了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总让神结留在国内
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真拿这孩子没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白皇大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹的所作所为 实在太抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样的处罚都由我来承受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 恳请对这孩子从宽处理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没打算那么小题大做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你的妹妹 也能让我们以宾客的身份招待吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么神结也可以待在这里喽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣上 这些也请您过目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋别抢我路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才给我滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总大将
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长 帮我多添点兵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后的战局将会被机动力所左右
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 能多添些坐骑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有一个身体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么都来这里了还要学习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你不太懂礼节呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神结我可不会认输
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不赖嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪儿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 公主殿下不是应该在学习中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了 不要告诉姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.55,0:15:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有打算去告诉她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也正处在工作时间 但溜了出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又…这样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 要怎么才能和那女孩变得好起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个身边带着大东西的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说阿露露啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想和她交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就破例告诉你一个秘法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘法？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘法 自然就得保密了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.88,0:16:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:17:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是客人吗 请原谅我以这种形式相见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫柚叶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫神结 多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧 看到过圣上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没见到过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙特阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下她…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 说的是她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙特还真是杞人忧天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎柚叶阁下也一起乘在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚叶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:18:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚叶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会觉得无聊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有一股令我感到很怀念的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图斯克尔大人的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您认识祖母吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡是以药师为目标的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有一个不知道图斯克尔大人的名字的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我很想再拜见一次 请她指教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们死后是被招至大神那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但生死离别 始终是让人难过的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你回忆起伤心事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 已经不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.03,0:19:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经过去了 而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.22,0:19:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…要是一直难过下去的话 会被奶奶批评的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 尽管伤心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤心的时候就应该好好痛快伤心一场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤心了之后再继续前进 也为时不晚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 穆库鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.15,0:20:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再忍一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望这样的日子能持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和图斯克尔国的人们相处了以后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们充分了解到 这国家已经和处在前朝统治下的时候不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.62,0:20:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白皇大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们今后也可以一直保持友好的往来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们应该说的 一起努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小阿露 小柚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和你们交上朋友我真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还会再来玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.53,0:21:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见


